{{作品名稱|name=''Grace of Monaco''|cn=摩纳哥王妃|hk=cn|tw=為愛璀璨：永遠的葛麗絲}}為2014年美国和法国发行的一部关于前好莱坞传奇影星[[格蕾丝·凯莉|格蕾丝·凯莉]]的[[传记电影|传记电影]]，由[[奥利维埃·达昂|奥利维埃·达昂]]（Olivier Dahan）导演。奥斯卡影后[[妮可·基德曼|妮可·基德曼]]主演。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://gma.yahoo.com/video/movies-26594261/nicole-kidman-plays-grace-kelly-in-upcoming-film-grace-of-monaco-30799189.html |title=Nicole Kidman Plays Grace Kelly in Upcoming Film 'Grace of Monaco' – Yahoo!<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2014-07-21 |archive-date=2012-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121030060128/http://gma.yahoo.com/video/movies-26594261/nicole-kidman-plays-grace-kelly-in-upcoming-film-grace-of-monaco-30799189.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>其他演员包括[[弗兰克·兰格拉|弗兰克·兰格拉]]、[[帕克·波西|帕克·波西]]、[[德里克·雅各比|德里克·雅各比]]、[[帕兹·维嘉|帕兹·维嘉]]、[[罗杰·阿什顿-格里菲斯|罗杰·阿什顿-格里菲斯]]、[[米洛·文提米利亚|米洛·文提米利亚]]和[[蒂姆·罗斯|蒂姆·罗斯]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thehollywoodnews.com/2012/08/16/tim-roth-cast-in-grace-of-monaco/ |title=Tim Roth Cast In ‘Grace Of Monaco’ – The Hollywood News<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2014-07-21 |archive-date=2020-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200511110203/http://www.thehollywoodnews.com/2012/08/16/tim-roth-cast-in-grace-of-monaco/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dreammoviecast.com/casting-news/tim-roth-joins-grace-of-monaco-alongside-nicole-kidman-and-frank-langella |title=Tim Roth Joins ‘Grace of Monaco’ Alongside Nicole Kidman and Frank Langella (UPDATE: Parker Posey & Milo Ventimiglia Join) {{!}} Dream TV & Movie Casting News – DreamMovieCast<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2014-07-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150103071959/http://www.dreammoviecast.com/casting-news/tim-roth-joins-grace-of-monaco-alongside-nicole-kidman-and-frank-langella |archive-date=2015-01-03 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

原定2013年11月底第一次发行上映，但由于发行方韦恩斯坦公司与导演关于影片最终剪辑版本存在巨大争议，预定上映日期一再推迟到2014年3月14日，<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/race/nicole-kidmans-grace-monaco-pushed-634780|title=Weinstein Co. Moves Nicole Kidman's 'Grace of Monaco' Out of 2013 Contention (Exclusive)|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|accessdate=September 24, 2013|first=Scott|last=Feinberg|date=September 23, 2013|archive-date=2021-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210212094631/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/race/nicole-kidmans-grace-monaco-pushed-634780|dead-url=no}}</ref>但不足两个月便再度被无限期延迟。<ref>{{cite web |author=Posted January 23rd, 2014 8:00PM |url=http://news.moviefone.com/2014/01/23/nicole-kidman-grace-of-monaco-release/ |title=Nicole Kidman's 'Grace of Monaco' Pulled From Release Following Epic Creative Clash - The Moviefone Blog |work=News.moviefone.com |date=2014-01-23 |accessdate=2014-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140519131513/http://news.moviefone.com/2014/01/23/nicole-kidman-grace-of-monaco-release |archive-date=2014-05-19 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-25878770 | work=BBC News | title=Princess Grace movie pulled from release schedule | date=January 24, 2014 | accessdate=2014-07-21 | archive-date=2019-11-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191105030824/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-25878770 | dead-url=no }}</ref>影片最后在2014年5月14日作为[[2014年戛纳电影节|第67届戛纳国际电影节]]的开幕影片，在卢米埃尔大厅做国际首映。<ref name="MonacoCannes">{{cite web |url=http://www.festival-cannes.fr/en/article/60489.html |title=Grace of Monaco by Olivier Dahan to open the 67th Festival de Cannes |accessdate=25 January 2014 |work=Cannes |archive-date=2015-07-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150708192345/http://www.festival-cannes.fr/en/article/60489.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Cannes">{{cite news |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/grace-monaco-open-cannes-film-673769 |title='Grace of Monaco' to Open Cannes Film Festival |accessdate=24 January 2014 |work=Hollywood Reporter |first=Rhonda |last=Richford |archive-date=2015-07-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150705071952/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/grace-monaco-open-cannes-film-673769 |dead-url=no }}</ref>英国的首映在2014年6月4日，6月6日开始全球发行。

==剧情==
1962年，格蕾丝（妮可·基德曼饰）大婚已经有六年，她的一颦一笑已经成为20世纪王妃的经典影像，但此时，她正在力图使自己的过去与现在和解。她渴望重返大银幕，却因为如今身兼三职——两个孩子的母亲、欧洲公国的王妃、[[雷尼埃三世|雷尼埃三世]]（蒂姆·罗斯饰）的妻子——而踌躇不前。
[[亞佛烈德·希區考克|亞佛烈德·希區考克]]（罗杰·阿什顿-格里菲斯饰）建议她重返[[好莱坞|好莱坞]]，与他合作拍摄[[艳贼_(电影)|艳贼]]（Marnie），这个提议令格蕾丝陷入苦恼。当时丈夫雷尼埃的现代化改革措施遭到了[[法国总统|法国总统]][[戴高乐|戴高乐]]的抵制，戴高乐要对摩纳哥课以重税，并推动武力以保证此措施得以实行。重返昔日明星之路，还是成为了一个彻彻底底的王室皇妃？格蕾丝面临选择......<ref name=autogenerated1>{{Cite web |url=http://www.lejdd.fr/Culture/Cinema/Actualite/Exclu-JDD-Olivier-Dahan-sur-la-polemique-autour-du-film-Grace-de-Monaco-Je-revendique-le-droit-a-la-fiction-586978 |title=Exclu JDD – Olivier Dahan, sur la polémique autour du film "Grace de Monaco" : "Je revendique le droit à la fiction" – leJDD.fr<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2014-07-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141027072735/http://www.lejdd.fr/Culture/Cinema/Actualite/Exclu-JDD-Olivier-Dahan-sur-la-polemique-autour-du-film-Grace-de-Monaco-Je-revendique-le-droit-a-la-fiction-586978 |archive-date=2014-10-27 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

